sequenceDiagram
    actor M as Manager
    participant UI as YogaApp UI
    participant API as API Server
    participant DB as MongoDB

    M->>UI: Enter instructor name
    UI->>API: POST /instructors/check-name
    API->>DB: Check for duplicate name
    DB-->>API: Results

    alt Duplicate found
        API-->>UI: Show warning
        M->>UI: Confirm or cancel
    end

    M->>UI: Fill remaining fields and submit
    UI->>API: POST /instructors
    API->>DB: Save instructor
    DB-->>API: Saved record
    API-->>UI: Confirmation message